446),o=e.i(821332),s=e.i(326917);let l=[{id:"destroy_lonely-how-u-feel",title:"How U Feel",artist:"Destroy Lonely",externalUrl:null,syncedLyrics:"[00:01.00] Some say, \"Nightmares are dreams perverted\"\n[00:07.27] I told them, \"It wasn't a nightmare,\" but they don't believe me\n[00:15.33] Huh (huh?), how you feel? (How you feel?)\n[00:17.76] Baby, I feel fine (I feel fine)\n[00:19.37] I need more dollar signs, but you came right on time\n[00:22.81] Can we turn off all these lights?\n[00:24.79] Can I roll up, get a lil' high?\n[00:26.43] Every time I look in your eyes, I look away mesmerized\n[00:30.22] And you shine brighter than the stars that decorate the night sky (Yeah)\n[00:33.97] And all I rock is flawless diamonds, I hope you don't mind\n[00:37.23] And I promise to keep you close, if you promise you're mine\n[00:40.93] And I been lapped them, no, it's not close, I crossed the finish line\n[00:44.54] Yeah, I look like a supermodel, and all my draws is Calvin Klein\n[00:48.23] Yeah, my baby, she built like a bottle\n[00:49.69] And I'm finna take a sip right now\n[00:51.79] Yeah, I'm pourin' some lines out the bottle\n[00:53.39] And I'm finna take a sip right now\n[00:55.26] Yeah, and I probably won't see you tomorrow\n[00:56.86] 'Cause I'm finna take a trip right now\n[00:59.03] Yeah, I've been gone\n[01:01.14] I lost my mind, and I'm tryna find my way back home\n[01:04.44] Baby, I'm the real Rolling Stone\n[01:05.82] I've been changed, I don't do phones\n[01:07.67] I won't talk until the case closed\n[01:09.48] Fuck 12, nigga, free my bros\n[01:11.31] I got a problem with keeping my clothes\n[01:13.24] And all my swag, they stole\n[01:15.00] You can keep it, I don't want it\n[01:16.87] And I'd throw all this shit away\n[01:18.26] If I can't give it to none of my homies\n[01:20.37] And I'd throw all this shit away\n[01:21.77] If I can't give none of it to my bitches\n[01:24.13] If a nigga talk down on my gang\n[01:25.40] Then he gon' leave here with some stitches (huh)\n[01:27.83] Huh (Huh?), how you feel? (How you feel?)\n[01:30.40] Baby, I feel fine (I feel fine)\n[01:32.02] I need more dollar signs, but you came right on time\n[01:35.33] Can we turn off all these lights?\n[01:37.34] Can I roll up, get a lil' high?\n[01:39.14] Every time I look in your eyes, I look away mesmerized\n[01:42.71] And you shine brighter than the stars that decorate the night sky (Yeah)\n[01:46.46] And all I rock is flawless diamonds, I hope you don't mind\n[01:50.08] And I promise to keep you close, if you promise you're mine\n[01:53.56] And I been lapped them, no, it's not close, I crossed the finish line\n[01:57.19] And I'm not tellin' lies\n[01:59.07] Got a mask on, no disguise\n[02:00.85] And the old me already died\n[02:02.68] Keep it on me, on my side\n[02:04.34] If you know me, know I'm fried\n[02:06.22] And I love you if you ridin'\n[02:08.02] And the doors in my brand new ride, go up, they suicide\n[02:11.68] I was geeked off all them Roxies, livin' on the top floor in the Roxy\n[02:15.37] And my life done' changed so promptly, cameras flashing, paparazzi\n[02:19.04] And I only sip on Wockhardt and Tris to make me nauseous\n[02:22.36] And I always go hard, these niggas going hardly (yes)\n[02:25.85] I just bought her Goyard, she ride me like a Harley (yes)\n[02:29.24] I told her she a superstar, and I just think she gnarly\n[02:32.30] Me and my gang in here, this a rich-nigga party\n[02:36.06] She brought her gang in here, this a bad-bitches party\n[02:39.71] I'm a raver but a real rockstar, please, can we get guitars?\n[02:43.27] I'm an alien but not from Mars\n[02:45.33] And these niggas trap too hard\n[02:47.08] She playin', baby, don't you start (huh)\n[02:49.11] Please don't make this hard\n[02:50.64] I go NBA, but I'm not Vince Carter\n[02:52.52] That just mean I'm ballin' and my money larger\n[02:54.71] Huh (huh?), how you feel? (How you feel?)\n[02:57.56] Baby, I feel fine (I feel fine)\n[02:59.36] I need more dollar signs, but you came right on time\n[03:02.65] Can we turn off all these lights?\n[03:04.51] Can I roll up, get a lil' high?\n[03:06.37] Every time I look in your eyes, I look away mesmerized\n[03:09.92] And you shine brighter than the stars that decorate the night sky (yeah)\n[03:13.79] And all I rock is flawless diamonds, I hope you don't mind\n[03:17.23] And I promise to keep you close, if you promise you're mine\n[03:20.82] And I been lapped them, no, it's not close, I crossed the finish line (the finish line)\n[03:24.97]",order:0,audio:{url:"https://assets.haunt.gg/songs/destroy_lonely-how-u-feel.mp3",mime:"audio/mpeg",width:null,height:null,duration:233},cover:{url:"https://assets.haunt.gg/songs/covers/destroy_lonely-how-u-feel.png",mime:"image/png",width:null,height:null,duration:null}},{id:"playboi_carti-fomdj",title:"FOMDJ",artist:"Playboi Carti",externalUrl:null,syncedLyrics:"[00:00.68] (Wake up, F1LTHY)\n[00:04.39] You got to\n[00:06.05] \n[00:28.17] I got me a natural lil' bitch, I'll fuck that lil' ho on her B-Day\n[00:31.54] I'ma walk on stage, my eyes so red, yeah, fuck what she say\n[00:35.04] I been on the E-way\n[00:36.64] Bitch, come on the G-way\n[00:38.38] She wanna put on my chain, yeah\n[00:40.16] She wanna fuck on my DJ\n[00:41.89] Let it go like a relay\n[00:43.39] Fuck her mouth, I don't do dates\n[00:45.14] All this money, I'm big paid\n[00:46.87] Buy a Richard, a new Wraith\n[00:48.60] Oh yeah\n[00:50.28] Give my opps they due dates\n[00:52.18] Crash out for the gang, hol' up\n[00:53.81] Crash out for a mixtape\n[00:55.58] Have you fuck on my peers\n[00:57.10] I'ma hit all the gears\n[00:58.95] Have you switchin' your lips\n[01:00.45] Yeah, she got all the skills\n[01:02.25] And I'm still on the hill\n[01:03.87] Yeah, I'm still in The Hills\n[01:05.68] We ain't missed a meal, we ain't missed a meal\n[01:12.75] We ain't missed a meal, we ain't missed a meal\n[01:19.28] This how the Perky feel, this how the ecstasy feel\n[01:22.67] This how the 